<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Time Capsule</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="bg-white shadow-md py-2 px-8 flex justify-between items-center fixed top-0 w-full z-50 ">
        <div class="flex items-center">
            <img src="/images/background1.png" alt="Virtual Time Capsule" class="w-6 h-6 object-contain">
            <span class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-700">Time Capsule</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-x-6">
            <a href="/" class="nav-link text-gray-700 hover:text-blue-600 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl">Home</a>
            <a href="/story" class="nav-link text-gray-700 hover:text-blue-600 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl">Our Story</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="nav-link text-gray-700 hover:text-blue-600 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl">Contact Us</a>
            <a href="/login" class="bg-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl">Get Started</a>
        </div>
        
        <script>
            // Get current path
            const currentPath = window.location.pathname;
            
            // Select all nav links
            document.querySelectorAll(".nav-link").forEach(link => {
                if (link.getAttribute("href") === currentPath) {
                    link.classList.add("relative", "after:absolute", "after:left-0", "after:w-full", "after:h-0.5", "after:bg-blue-700", "after:bottom-0", "after:scale-x-0", "after:transition-transform", "after:duration-300", "after:ease-in-out");
                    setTimeout(() => {
                        link.classList.add("after:scale-x-100");
                    }, 100);
                }
            });
        </script>
        
        
        
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="relative w-full">
        <img src="/images/background2.png" alt="Virtual Time Capsule" class="w-full h-auto">
        <div class="absolute top-1/3 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 bg-black bg-opacity-50 px-8 py-6 rounded-lg">
            <h1 class="text-white text-5xl font-bold text-center">Want to send a message to the future?</h1>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 px-10 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-blue-600 text-5xl font-bold mx-auto max-w-2xl">Capture your most meaningful moments and schedule them for a nostalgic surprise in the future.</h1>
        <h1 class="text-gray-600 mt-5 text-3xl px-8 py-8 ">The best way to safeguard memories and deliver messages to the future. Whether you're commemorating a milestone, sharing wisdom across generations, or preserving cherished family traditions.</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center items-center mt-10">
        <img src="/images/background3.png" alt="Virtual Time Capsule" class="w-3/4 h-98">
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-16">
        <h2 class=" text-6xl font-bold text-blue-600">Who & Why</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-12 mt-12">
        <div class="text-center w-64">
            <img src="/images/background4.png" alt="Families" class="w-48 h-48 object-cover rounded-full mx-auto transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl duration-300 ease-out">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-700 mt-4">Future Life Events</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">Hold onto every precious memory before it fades, and send it back when they’re older.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center w-64">
            <img src="/images/background5.png" alt="Students" class="w-48 h-48 object-cover rounded-full mx-auto transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl duration-300 ease-out">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-700 mt-4">Moments with Family</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">Future birthdays, holidays, celebrations, & weddings- keep those memories alive for years.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center w-64">
            <img src="/images/background6.png" alt="Legacy" class="w-48 h-48 object-cover rounded-full mx-auto transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl duration-300 ease-out">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-700 mt-4">Student Life</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">Capture growth, dreams, and early journeys as you navigate into who you want to be.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center w-64">
            <img src="/images/background7.png" alt="Legacy" class="w-48 h-48 object-cover rounded-full mx-auto transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl duration-300 ease-out">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-700 mt-4">Last Letter Goodbye</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">Even when you’re no longer by their side, continue to share your love, wisdom, and memories.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class=" bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-purple-700 relative  py-10 px-10 text-center w-3/4 h-3/4 mx-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg mt-8">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">If you could send a message to the future...</p>
        <div class="flex justify-center mt-10">
            <img src="/images/background8.png" alt="Send a Message to the Future" class="transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl duration-300 ease-out w-3/4 h-3/4 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        </div>
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-10">What it would be...</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials Section -->
<div class="bg-gray-100 py-12 px-6">
    
    <!-- Section Title -->
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-10">Real Stories, Lasting Memories</h2>
    
    <!-- Grid Layout for Testimonials -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">

        <!-- Testimonial Cards -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl duration-300 ease-out">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">A Message to My Future Grandchildren</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 italic">
                "In my 80s, I know I won’t be here forever. I wanted my grandchildren to know me—to hear my voice and learn our family history. Virtual Time Capsule made that possible. I recorded my stories, advice, and birthday messages I won’t be around to celebrate. My great-grandkids will always know who I was."
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-900 font-bold">— Betty L., 82, Arizona</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl duration-300 ease-out">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">My Daughter’s First Steps—Saved Forever</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 italic">
                "Life as a mom is chaotic—I barely have time to sit down, let alone organize memories. Virtual Time Capsule made it effortless. I saved my daughter’s first steps, first words, and first laugh—all in one place. Someday, she’ll see those moments exactly as they happened."
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-900 font-bold">— Melissa C., 34, Texas</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl duration-300 ease-out">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">A Birthday Surprise From My Future Self</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 italic">
                "At 18, I recorded a message for my 30-year-old self, thinking it was silly. When I finally received it, I was speechless. My younger self reminded me of dreams, fears, and lessons I had forgotten. Watching it, I realized how much I’ve grown—it was like getting advice from my past."
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-900 font-bold">— Olivia H., 30, Illinois</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl duration-300 ease-out">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">A Message From My Father, Even as He Forgot Who I Was</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 italic">
                "When my father was diagnosed with Alzheimer’s, I thought I had lost him forever. But before he got sick, he recorded a Virtual Time Capsule. In it, he spoke to my future self, reminding me of our stories, his love, and his laughter. Even though he forgot me, I’ll never forget him."
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-900 font-bold">— Lisa P., 34, Texas</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl duration-300 ease-out">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">A Message from My Mom, Two Years After She Passed</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 italic">
                "Before my mom passed away, she started a Virtual Time Capsule. Two years later, I received my first message from her. Seeing her face, hearing her voice—it felt like she was right there with me. It wasn’t just a video; it was a gift of presence when I needed it most."
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-900 font-bold">— Sarah M., 28, New York</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl duration-300 ease-out">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">A Message From My Late Husband on Our 50th Anniversary</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 italic">
                "On what would have been our 50th anniversary, I received a Virtual Time Capsule from my late husband. He had recorded it years before, knowing he might not be here. Watching it, I felt his love, his jokes, and our life together all over again. I replay it often, and every time, I feel him with me."
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-900 font-bold">— Margaret W., 72, Florida</p>
        </div>

    </div>

</div>

<footer class="bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-purple-700 py-6 text-center text-white">
    <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
        <img src="/images/background1.png" alt="Virtual Time Capsule Logo" class="h-16">
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm">&copy; 2025  Time Capsule LLC. All Rights Reserved.</p>
</footer>


    
    
    
</body>
</html>
